object.customQuery:
SELECT distinct account.SystemId, account.ParentId, account.CMMContainer, account.Id, account.UpdateCount, account.UpdateUser, account.UpdateTimestamp, account.AccountPrevRef, account.AccountNextRef, account.TypeCd, account.AccountNumber, account.AccountDisplayNumber, account.CustomerRef, account.StatusCd, account.IndexName, account.ProductVersionCd, account.InstallmentPlan, account.BillToCd, account.ProviderCode, account.ProviderName, account.PrintInvoiceInd, account.PaidInd, account.PayPlanCd, account.CancelCd, account.CommissionRate, account.WrittenAmt, account.CommissionAmt, account.NetAmt, account.OpenAmt, account.UnbilledAmt, account.TotalAmt, account.PaidAmt, account.AdjustmentAmt, account.CreditAmt, account.CarryDt, account.CancelDt, account.NoticeDt, account.CycleCd, account.NextCycleActionCd, account.NextCycleActionDt, account.NextCycleActionDesc, account.ReceiptOnLegalInd, account.ReceiptOnCancelInd, account.Version, account.NetOpenAmt, account.NetTotalAmt, account.NetPaidAmt, account.NetAdjustmentAmt, account.NetUnbilledAmt, account.ActivatedInd, account.BillingEntityCarryDt, account.BillingEntitySequenceNumber, account.BillingEntityTypeCd, account.VIPLevel, account.PreviousCancelCd, account.AuditAccountInd, account.StatementAccountRef, account.RowId 
FROM
 account
where systemid in (select SystemId from advrxxchangedbeans where concat(adddt,addtm)>='$$m_strtdt' and concat(adddt,addtm) <='$$m_Enddt' and
 cmmcontainer='Account') and account.cmmcontainer='Account'
